  "3253860": {
    "name": "Gallery: Coloring book & decor",
    "steam_appid": 3253860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/71a74fe62bd386ea69406656663d2fc5.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/71a74fe62bd386ea69406656663d2fc5.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/71a74fe62bd386ea69406656663d2fc5.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绘画、翻新、装饰、跟随故事并注意：Gallery 是第一个可以通过数字上色并同时享受家居设计和装饰的涂色书游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f0880fe70ed16f4431960d4998685527.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/f0880fe70ed16f4431960d4998685527.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的英雄米娅和里奥的精彩冒险：为数百幅图片上色，翻新一座旧房子，让它充满生机和精美的装饰，修复一座被遗弃的艺术画廊，沉浸在这对可爱情侣的生动故事中吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/dd0bb386a8d3fa293c5445e2ea17d7ac.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/dd0bb386a8d3fa293c5445e2ea17d7ac.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百幅独特的高质量画作是为Gallery独家创作的。原创玩法：结合了涂色书和家居设计！为图片上色，获得星星，并用它们来装饰房子和探索故事。这是一款为真正设计师打造的创意游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/4357b82392c5b81a63351d5f04282c42.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/4357b82392c5b81a63351d5f04282c42.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有多种场景供探索和翻新。我们这里有适合各种口味的温馨角落！丰富多样的装饰：每个房间和其他场景都有不止一个选项可供选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/35ba71ae9b442fb92fd9c71d6c3280e0.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/35ba71ae9b442fb92fd9c71d6c3280e0.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米娅和里奥有多种不同的服装。想让米娅变身为古代公主、电影明星或赛车技师吗？没问题！想让里奥穿上巨大的火鸡装、跳舞服或消防员制服吗？我们应有尽有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/957c7c85d459186699d651ea0ae20eef.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/957c7c85d459186699d651ea0ae20eef.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里不会有失败！没有“游戏结束”的提示！您所要做的就是为图片上色，放松并享受故事。我们还有众多游戏内活动等待着玩家，您可以获得新的独家画作进行上色、装饰元素进行安装，甚至还有宠物供您…抚摸！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总而言之，拿起画笔，放松身心，让我们一起把这个世界描绘得五彩缤纷吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/27dc03e3c970016657eec5b3d23972a0.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/27dc03e3c970016657eec5b3d23972a0.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p>",
